В качестве БД предполагается использовать postgres для обсепечения согласованности данных и атомарности.

Place:
id: uuid
name: str
address: str (full address)
address_city: str
host: uuid (user id)
created_at: datetime
status: text ("created", "deleted")


Watch:
id: uuid
host: uuid (user id)
filmwork: uuid
place_id: uuid
time: datetime
seats: int
price: float (or decimal)
status: text (eg "created", "canceled", ...)
created_at: datetime


Reservation:
id: uuid
watch_id: uuid
participant_id: uuid
created_at: datetime
status: text ("created", "canceled")
seats: int
modified_at: datetime
